Name: Dodge It! 2
About the game: Welcome In The Universe Of Dodge it! In this infinite game you will need to collect the most white circles without touching the red circles but BEWARE! For each white circles you collect a red circles will appear. Don't touch it or you will die! Features Random Spawn Powerups (spawn every 10 scores) Blue Ball = Shield Pink Ball = Slow Time Green Ball = Score x2 Online Leaderboard Steam inventory Achievement Multiplayer Online Chat Game Mode
